name: 東条悠希
commentary: Athletic type like the main character of shonen manga. She has a passionate personality when she sets a goal, and she is proud of her ability to go all over the country in her favorite soccer. She is not good at acting cute. Her dream is to become a national idol.
character_designer_serie: <Monogatari> Series, "Fireworks, Should You See It from the Bottom or the Side?"
